Post.title: Adb
Post._content:
#### 1. 
```
adb devices #

adb -s cf123456 shell # 

adb install test.apk # 

adb install -r demo.apk #apk sd 

adb uninstall cn.com.test.mobile #

adb uninstall -k cn.com.test.mobile #app 

adb shell pm list packages #app 

adb shell pm list packages -3 #

adb shell pm clear cn.com.test.mobile #

adb shell am start -ncn.com.test.mobile/.ui.SplashActivity #

adb shell dumpsys package #Package Information

adb shell dumpsys meminfo #Memory Usage

adb shell am force-stop cn.com.test.mobile #

adb logcat #

adb logcat -c #log 

adb logcat *:W #warn

adb reboot #

adb shell top -s 10 #10 app

adb push <local> <remote> #

adb pull <remote> <local> #

adb bugreport #bug 

adb help #ADB 
```

#### 2.&
```
adb shell getprop ro.build.version.release  Android 

adb shell getprop ro.product.model  

adb shell dumpsys battery   

adb get-serialno    

adb shell wm size   

adb shell wm density    

adb shell settings get secure android_id  android_id

adb shell -> su -> service call iphonesubinfo 1    IMEI

adb shell cat /sys/class/net/wlan0/address  Mac,

adb shell cat /proc/cpuinfo     CPU 

adb shell cat /proc/meminfo     

adb shell cat /system/build.prop    

adb shell ps    

adb shell pm list packages  app 

adb shell pm list packages -s   

adb shell pm list packages -3   

adb shell pm list packages | find "test" win    test

adb shell pm list packages | grep test linux  test

adb shell cat /sys/class/net/wlan0/address MAC , 

adb shell dumpsys activity services [<packagename>] Services

<packagename> <packagename> ServicesServices

<packagename> adb shell dumpsys activity services com.tencentcom.tencent.weixincom.tencent.qq Services 
```

#### 3.

```
adb install <apkfile> apkfile .apk 

adb install -r test.apk apk

adb install -s test.apk apksd

adb uninstall -k com.test.mobile    app 

adb shell pm uninstall -k --user 0 <packagename> 

```

#### 4.
```
adb start-server

adb kill-server

adb -P <port> start-server  adb server port 5037
```

#### 5.
```
adb shell pm clear <packagename>  

adb shell am force-stop <packagename>   

adb shell am start -n com.tencent.mm/.ui.LauncherUI     activity

adb shell am startservice -n com.tencent.mm/.plugin.accountsync.model.AccountAuthenticatorService   Service

adb shell am broadcast -a android.intent.action.BOOT_COMPLETED    BOOT_COMPLETED ()

adb shell am broadcast -a android.intent.action.BOOT_COMPLETED -n org.mazhuang.boottimemeasure/.BootCompletedReceiver BOOT_COMPLETED

adb shell am broadcast -a com.android.action.PLAY -p com.android.car -f 0x00000020 --es BACKGROUND 'FALSE' 
```
#### 6./
```
adb shell input keyevent 26  #
adb shell input keyevent 82  #
adb shell input keyevent 3  #HOME 
adb shell input keyevent 4 #
adb shell input keyevent 24 #
adb shell input keyevent 25 #
adb shell input keyevent 164 #
adb shell input keyevent 85  #/
adb shell input keyevent 86 #
adb shell input keyevent 87 #
adb shell input keyevent 88 #
adb shell input keyevent 126 #
adb shell input keyevent 127 #
adb shell input keyevent 224 #
adb shell input keyevent 223 #
adb shell input swipe 300 1000 300 500  #
# 300 1000 300 500 x y x y 
adb shell input text hello #
```

#### 7.
##### 
```
adb exec-out screencap -p > img.png     #exec-out

adb shell screencap -p /sdcard/img.png      #

-p  png 

```
##### 
```
adb shell screenrecord /sdcard/filename.mp4
```
##### WiFi
```
/data/misc/wifi/WifiConfigStore.xml
```
##### 
```
adb reboot recovery     Recovery
```

##### 
```
adb logcat -c && adb logcat >log.txt

adb logcat *:E >log.txt

ANR
1.adb pull data/anr/traces.txt
2.adb bugreport C:\Users\summer\Desktop
```

##### App

```
adb shell start -S -W com.example.camera/.MainActivity
```

Post.title: Android
Post._content:
**java**
```
udo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk
export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64
export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH
export CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tools.jar
java -version
```

****

```
sudo apt-get install git  gnupg flex bison gperf build-essential zip curl zlib1g-dev gcc-multilib g++-multilib libc6-dev-i386 lib32ncurses-dev x11proto-core-dev libx11-dev lib32z1-dev libgl1-mesa-dev libxml2-utils xsltproc unzip python libtinfo5 libncurses5-dev libncurses5 u-boot-tools
```




****

- Ensure Jack service is installed and started
```
1./etc/java-8-openjdk/security/java.securityjdk.tls.disabledAlgorithmsTLSv1, TLSv1.1 ;

2.jack 
cd prebuilts/sdk/tools
./jack-admin start-server/stop-server/kill-server
```



- lex:aidl<=system/tools/aidl/aidl_language_I.II FAILED:/

```
export LC_ALL=C
```

**framework.jar**

```
out/target/common/obj/JAVA_LIBRARIES/framework_intermediates/classes.jar
```
